title: ASUS rolls out stable Android 12 update to the ROG Phone 5 and ROG Phone 5S
content:
After rolling out a stable Android 12 update to the ZenFone 8 in December, ASUS is now extending the latest version of Android to two more phones in its portfolio: ROG Phone 5 and ROG Phone 5S. ASUS had previously promised to update both phones to Android 12 in Q1 2022 and the company is

The post ASUS rolls out stable Android 12 update to the ROG Phone 5 and ROG Phone 5S appeared first on xda-developers.
description: As per announcements on ZenTalk forums, ASUS has started rolling out a stable Android 12 update to the ROG Phone 5 and ROG Phone 5S.
